{"tid":1748654,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"買機票係需要一份勇氣","createTime":"2019-11-23T19:02:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T04:51:29.000Z","uid":140115,"like":23,"dislike":105,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"b84356e78d2eecedbc78f04bba89aff03b099c44","tid":1748654,"uid":140115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:02:44.000Z","msg":"有無人明白買機票係需要幾多嘅勇氣？<br />\n<br />\n係人都會睇機票 次次睇完就當買左會去咁<br />\n但買機票係需要一份破釜沉舟嘅勇氣<br />\n當你俾左錢就一定要去 當你確定左就無得退錢<br />\n同時間你都承受唔起蝕左酒店錢<br />\n然後嗰段日子無論發生咩事都唔可以出現<br />\n所以就個人而言 每次想買機票去旅行都會左諗右諗<br />\n向呢個不停瞻前顧後嘅情況下<br />\n我最後都係㩒左「取消」<br />\n無買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人可以話俾我聽<br />\n到底我呢d唔知擔心黎做咩嘅野係咪多餘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都想有一程話走就走 拎起個背囊就行得嘅旅行呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e2dbc834b6793b39d1d9ab42ccd0317493fa7ed","tid":1748654,"uid":96,"like":155,"dislike":0,"score":155,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:04:59.000Z","msg":"開啲咁撚on9嘅po仲大勇氣"},{"pid":"23f69ca2f1445b63cf4d83412273ac65a2d8ef5f","tid":1748654,"uid":198535,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:06:32.000Z","msg":"屌你老母都需要一份勇氣"},{"pid":"cc50d4a51192ac5b74afe31ba875acef66085885","tid":1748654,"uid":148002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4e2dbc834b6793b39d1d9ab42ccd0317493fa7ed","tid":1748654,"uid":96,"like":155,"dislike":0,"score":155,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:04:59.000Z","msg":"開啲咁撚on9嘅po仲大勇氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:07:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029fc9eaf82c18b423504af8b4eaa2dd6246203a","tid":1748654,"uid":219635,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T19:08:24.000Z","msg":"比人屌都要出post都係勇氣"},{"pid":"0789a0650c217f85f59681